Python-Guitar-Transcription-Aid
===============================

This is a python program that helps transcribing guitar music by drawing spectrum onto a fretboard. It is currently in a very early development state.

Requirements (Ubuntu):
python
python-matplotlib
python-gtk2
python-pygoocanvas
python-gst0.10
python-gst0.10-dev
gstreamer0.10-plugins-bad
build-essentials
python-gobject
python-scipy
python-cairo

Building:
cd SpectrumVisualizerBase
python setup.py build
